<HEAD>Rider Pleads Guilty To Cantering While Intoxicated</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ELLICOTT CITY, Md. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A 31-year-old man seen swaying on the
back of a horse while riding down a crowded sidewalk was ordered to
spend 45 days in jail after pleading guilty to drunken driving.
   Oscar Fincham of Ellicott City took up horseback riding to get
