   A colorful, 3{-hour spectacle mixing ancient Korean rituals with
space-age technology kicked off 16 days of athletic competition at
the Seoul Summer Games. The Games will provide a showcase for South
Korea and produce the first all-out East-West gold rush since the
1976 Montreal Games.
